  <section id="work" class="about-sec">
    <h2>Work with me</h2>
    <p>
      I'm targeting remote US and Canadian teams hiring for Senior or Staff
      Embedded Linux Engineer, Platform Engineer, or Firmware Architect roles.
      The best fit is a connected device or industrial product where the team
      needs ownership below the application: Yocto/OpenEmbedded, BSPs, Linux
      integration, networking, security, and field reliability.
    </p>
    <p>
      I can also be useful on adjacent systems roles where C/C++, Linux
      internals, graphics, WebAssembly, or low-level debugging matter more than
      a conventional embedded title.
